.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, emerald, coral, apricot
1. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes emerald##2
2. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Color   | coral | orange | emerald | apricot |

 